sentences.sentence: I agree to provide the television and Entertainment Licensing Authority (TELA) with opinions on television and radio broadcasts and I have no objection to the handling of my personal data by TELA.
sentences.translation: 本人同意就电视及电台广播事宜向影视及娱乐事务管理处提供意见，并同意贵处对个人资料的处理。
